{"tid":567630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽高鐵擋門被列車員扯開　網民：大快人心","createTime":"2018-02-21T04:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T04:59:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c9ea4025c8145b2637faa7ad8270bc1d7f9a56","tid":567630,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/125652_9b98c22105a0012665a1fa5fc0973a05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F125652_9b98c22105a0012665a1fa5fc0973a05.png&h=38992339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地野蠻乘客為求一己之私，公然攔阻列車大門，造成班次延誤時有發生，網民對此惡行嗤之以鼻，也有不少野蠻人被罰款或者拘留，但始終無法根治這些人的「劣根性」。近日網絡又流傳一段大媽強行攔阻高鐵列車大門，結果被列車員一手扯開的短片，惟網民對於列車員這種「以暴制暴」的方式不僅沒有留言譴責，反而大讚「大快人心」。 <br />\n<br />\n網傳短片所見，大媽擋在高鐵列車的大門，期間不斷哀求工作人員通融等候，惟經工作人員多次勸說後，大媽依然「不為所動」企硬擋住車門，不肯讓開，最終一名在月台的列車員趁大媽不備之際，一手捉實其左手再大力一拉，將大媽扯出車外，而車廂內的乘務員隨即配合將車門關上，然而列車便駛離車站，結束鬧劇。 <br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180220/mobile/bkncn-20180220213149702-0220_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180220%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20180220213149702-0220_05011_001.html&d=aRUSysLZ%2BeaNkx2Uih%2FT4tU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=2ddfea68\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180220/mobile/bkncn-20180220213149702-0220_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"22d3fc68bc4fefdcfcdaa34b266028644f47dbe1","tid":567630,"uid":21423,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5ce8dd3f2f368a28bc4939325f10b2a6a381d25","tid":567630,"uid":85957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22d3fc68bc4fefdcfcdaa34b266028644f47dbe1","tid":567630,"uid":21423,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:58:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手撕鬼子啲friend"}]}